name: FROM OUT OF THE WAD BIN... 'Awaken'
description: I started working on this wad about 2+ years ago. The story was that you were abducted by aliens and taken into their space ship and slumped onto a metal table, ready to be meddled with. You woke up somehow (hence the title) and grabbed a gun off of the body of a policeman that was slumped onto a table next to you. AND SO BEGAN YOUR ALIEN KILLING SPREE...
